Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Perolehan/005 Terimaan Barang Perkhidmatan/001 Proses Kemasukan Terimaan Barang

Description: Open browser and navigate to Homepage URL
Click on Menu Sisi to display Menu selections
Kemasukan Terimaan Barang page loaded successfully
Click on drop - down No Dokumen
Set text RekodID based on the variable get from Pelulus page on Pesanan Tempatan
Click on No Dokumen from the result
Click on button cari to search for the record
Click on OK to close the prompt box

Double click on the field to make it editable
Input value for Dihantar using spinner - click until 5 times
Double click on the field to make it editable
Input value for Diterima using spinner - click until 5 times
